snippet.title: Open Carry In Maryland

localized.description:
Watch Delegate Smigiel use this video during testimony in Annapolis.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HR541Ea9n70

Maryland law regarding open carry of long arms is discussed here
https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=286617404828835&set=pb.150853305071913.-2207520000.1403750634.&type=3&theater
and here
https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=286617448162164&set=pb.150853305071913.-2207520000.1403750634.&type=3&permPage=1

Producing over 200 videos a year is expensive.  Please use the PayPal link below to donate toward the production of future videos.
https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=XBWG5HZ4K6FJ4

Warning:  Do not attempt to open carry in Maryland.

If attempted near law enforcement who do not know you or the law, you may be arrested or shot.

Delegate Smigiel knows the County Sheriff.

Please Note: Open carry of a handgun is completely illegal.

Open carry of long guns is cited at the bottom of page two and top of page three.
http://ia700501.us.archive.org/1/items/gov.uscourts.mdd.180772/gov.uscourts.mdd.180772.68.0.pdf
